N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5005.9 - Non-sufficient funds

State Regulations

If the commission receives notice that there are
non-sufficient funds to pay for any portion of a subscription purchase, the
portion of the attempted ticket purchase for which there are non-sufficient
funds shall be null and void. Notes
